         <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng" resp="part:emfr">
         	
<p>Prosperity! Fortune!</p>
<p>Year twenty-seven of the victorious king Nandivikramavarman.</p>
<p>Ceruvaliyār, son of Nāyakar Ataṭṭiyār, who fell in a cattle-raid at Curaikkuḷam in the Palkuṉrākkōṭṭam <supplied reason="explanation">and</supplied> in the Maṇṭaikuḷanāṭu, obtained a land.</p>

         </div>
         

